{"body": "From my commit.\n\n```ruby\n%x( psql #{config[db]['database']} -c \"CREATE EXTENSION hstore;\" 2>/dev/null ) # silence warning\n```\n\nMy fix had `2 > /dev/null`, so we can't display some warnings during installation.\nBut it keep running the specs (maybe).\n\nIf without `2 > /dev/null`, we display an another warning\n\n```\nsample=# CREATE EXTENSION hstore;\nWARNING: => is deprecated as an operator name\nDETAIL: This name may be disallowed altogether in future versions of PostgreSQL.\n```\n\n...\nI think we should remove `2 > /dev/null` and update the rails contributors guide about the above warning.\nWDYT ?", "url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rails/rails/issues/comments/6246070", "created_at": "2012-06-11T14:40:03Z", "html_url": "https://github.com/rails/rails/pull/6444#issuecomment-6246070", "updated_at": "2012-06-11T14:40:03Z", "repo": "rails", "issue_id": 6444, "user": {"following_url": "https://api.github.com/users/kennyj/following{/other_user}", "events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/kennyj/events{/privacy}", "organizations_url": "https://api.github.com/users/kennyj/orgs", "url": "https://api.github.com/users/kennyj", "gists_url": "https://api.github.com/users/kennyj/gists{/gist_id}", "html_url": "https://github.com/kennyj", "subscriptions_url": "https://api.github.com/users/kennyj/subscriptions", "avatar_url": "https://0.gravatar.com/avatar/1f0b221851379759360d7130dabdfa53?d=https%3A%2F%2Fidenticons.github.com%2F54ecc28e9508fcf28363014b0d1b4eb8.png", "repos_url": "https://api.github.com/users/kennyj/repos", "received_events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/kennyj/received_events", "gravatar_id": "1f0b221851379759360d7130dabdfa53", "starred_url": "https://api.github.com/users/kennyj/starred{/owner}{/repo}", "login": "kennyj", "type": "User", "id": 13426, "followers_url": "https://api.github.com/users/kennyj/followers"}, "owner": "rails", "_id": {"$oid": "523e58b2bd354364b900f491"}, "id": 6246070, "issue_url": "https://api.github.com/repos